{"Name":"Sophia Meadows","ShortName":"Sophia Meadows","Description":"Sophia Meadows is an exclusive 41-unit boutique development along Sophia Road sitting on a 13,783 sqft freehold site, offering low-density living in the heart of District 9. Its prime location places residents within walking distance of Dhoby Ghaut MRT interchange, and just minutes from the Orchard Shopping Belt. With both convenience \u0026 luxury seamlessly built together, it\u0027s perfect for both families and investors.","StartUrl":"/","Display":"standalone","BackgroundColor":"#ffffff","ThemeColor":"#041e42","Orientation":"portrait","Icons":[{"Src":"https://rtdbookappointment.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/Bookappointment/Property/046a2012-36eb-49f5-8ca7-29597bfe8dc0","Sizes":"192x192","Type":"image/png"},{"Src":"https://rtdbookappointment.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/Bookappointment/Property/046a2012-36eb-49f5-8ca7-29597bfe8dc0","Sizes":"512x512","Type":"image/png"}]}